Title: [ANN] NEWB - The crypto market's dirty little secret
Body: Raiden releases on Ethereum mainnet  https://medium.com/raiden-network/red-eyes-mainnet-release-announcement-d48235bbef3c   With Red Eyes, the first version of the Raiden Network has been successfully deployed on the Ethereum mainnet. The main goal of this release is to have the smart contracts and the core protocol battle tested on the mainnet. As part of ensuring this, a bug bounty was created specifically for the release.  *Opening, topping up, closing and settling of payment channels *Single and multi-hop transfers *Automatically joining a token network and opening channels with peers *REST API with endpoints for all functionalities *Redesigned WebUI *Raiden Explorer, visualizing the live status of the Network *Rewritten and more gas efficient smart contracts (e.g. only one contract per token network) *Improved protocol for dealing with edge cases *Recoverability in case of an irregular shutdown of the Raiden node *Integration of the Matrix transport protocol for messaging

Author: landomata
Title: [ANN] NEWB - The crypto market's dirty little secret
Body: The Newb platform is running in a stable mode with +99% uptime with users from around the world making thousands of posts about everything crypto.  But the team realizes that we are not where we need to be, the NEWB market situation makes it look as though we are losing.  We announced a concerted push to make marketing a core skill in our end of Q1 update. Yet the market situation kept trending negatively. Knowing that building a skill takes time we decided to devote a full year exclusively to this effort. The 1st two months of skill development has seen us revamp our brand image, position and messaging plus outlined plans to streamline the NEWB market from tokens listed on dual blockchains (NXT & ETH) to only one blockchain.   Since January all major crypto news platform has seen their traffic numbers decrease, please see data from Similarweb below for Coindesk, Cointelegraph & Us.

Author: landomata
Title: [ANN] NEWB - The crypto market's dirty little secret
Body: NEWB Coinmarketcap Status Update   NEWB has been a part of coinmarketcap for over 2 years which almost seems like forever. That changed this week when we were notified by community members that they could not find NEWB on coinmarketcap, we had been removed.  We immediately contacted coinmarketcap support to reverse the removal.  The support team responded that due to low volume the coins status was changed to inactive mode and would not appear as listed unless trade volumes increased.  Loss of coinmarketcap exposure is a negative for any crypto project but we decided to double down on our marketing skill development efforts. This added motivation has crystallized into a simple aim of becoming a world leading marketer. Once our marketing skills are world class we will be that much closer to reaching our long term goals.

Author: landomata
Title: [ANN] NEWB - The crypto market's dirty little secret
Body: We wanted to provide an urgent update regarding Newb in the Google Playstore.  We were notified today by Google that our app has been suspended from the playstore.  Our app was a progressive web app (PWA) modified so that it could be listed in the playstore.  It seems that Google was not happy with our modifications and removed the app.  I want to make it very clear PWA's are not suppose to live in the playstore but are to be installed directly from our site by Google.  The play store offered an additional distribution channel which in respect to PWA's was a step backward.    By installing the app directly from our site Google removes the need for users to search and find our app in the play store.  Now when a user visits https://chat.newbium.com using an Android phone he will be prompted to install our app.  The installation is done by Google and the app appears on the users phone as any app would if installed from the play store.  So although we would have preferred to be in the play store it does not change our situation very much.  Because we have build Newb chat as a progressive web app (PWA) we gain the advantage of a native app from the app stores without the need to actually be listed there.    If you want to test it out, please visit Newb chat @ https://chat.newbium.com and hit the install button when prompted or just click the install to homescreen button in your browser's settings.

Author: landomata
Title: [ANN] NEWB - The crypto market's dirty little secret
Body: Welcome to Newbistan   Newbium aka Newb has been steadily growing and building for over 2 years. But then it hit us like a freight train, no clear picture of what our long-term goals were for the project. We looked towards our mission, but mission didn't provide enough specifics to generate clarity. Necessity forced us to look elsewhere for specific long-term goals. The effort delivered, a 20 year goal of growing the Newb economy so that it enters the G20 largest economies. 5 year goal of crossing a billion market cap, and 1 year goal of reaching 50 cents per NEWB.

Author: landomata
Title: [ANN] NEWB - The crypto market's dirty little secret
Body: Newbium Brand Revolution Statement    Newbium at the core, it's core value is that we believe the world would be a better place if blockchain technology spreads to all human beings.  That's what we believe. And that providing cryptocurrency knowledge is essential. And so what we're going to do in our brand marketing campaigns going forward is to express that core value.  To communicate it to those striving for a better world.    To reflect this revolutionary change our new brand tagline for Newbium will be "The market's dirty little secret".  This message builds on and reinforces Newbium strength as one of the leading sources of cryptocurrency market and coin information in the world.  We feel this long-term campaign will help Newbium to stand out in an ever crowded marketplace.

Author: landomata
Title: [ANN] NEWB - The crypto market's dirty little secret
Body: Announcement - Making NEWB Market More Simple    Although, we tried very hard to keep NEWB on C-Cex exchange unfortunately C-Cex decided to delist us. Far from being a negative this event opens up a great opportunity for us to simplify the NEWB market.    Since the beginning NEWB tokens have existed on two separate blockchains. 51% of tokens on NXT Blockchain and 49% of tokens on Ethereum blockchain.  This situation was complicated and caused confusion for the community.  To fix this problem we plan to migrate both the 51% of NEWB on NXT and 49% of NEWB on ETH into a single Ethereum token with 100% of coins or 100 million tokens.    This move will bring major benefits for our community:  1. One Wallet (Ethereum). 2. NEWB market becomes united. 3. Marketing becomes easier. 4. NEWB token integration into Newbium platform becomes easier.   Timeframe: 4 months  We plan to complete the migration before September 30th, 2018.  The majority of the time will be taken up with R&D specifically contract code but also deep study of new ERC standards for example ERC777.    NEWB_NXT to NEWB_ETH Swap  If you have NEWB token on NXT blockchain or on C-Cex exchange then you will need to swap your tokens for NEWB tokens on Ethereum blockchain.  Please see the swap instructions here: https://coins.newbium.com/post/16034-newb_nxt-to-newb_eth-swap

Author: landomata
Title: [ANN] NEWB - The crypto market's dirty little secret
Body: We want to provide a brief update on the development work which we have been conducting over the past 3-4 weeks.  To provide an overview Google has finally announced that they will be migrating a very large number of sites to their Mobile First Index within the next 4 to 6 weeks.    Info on mobile first index: https://www.searchenginejournal.com/googles-mobile-first-indexing-what-it-is-how-you-can-prepare/212104/ Latest Google announcement: https://searchengineland.com/google-move-sites-mobile-first-index-within-next-several-weeks-292660  The Google mobile first index is the 1st time Google has changed how it is going to rank sites since the Search engine started.  Google has been preparing for this for over 3 years now and have been actively letting us know since 2017 that this change was coming so that we can prepare.  So to make sure we get in the mobile first index early we have been completing these recent updates which are partly focused on mobile usability and friendliness. One example of results from our work is the reduction of the size of https://coins.newbium.com by 25%.

Author: landomata
Title: [ANN] NEWB - The crypto market's dirty little secret
Body: NEWB tokens exist on two blockchains (NXT & Ethereum blockchains).  The NEWB on C-Cex is on NXT blockchain and the NEWB on IDEX is on Ethereum blockchain.  That is why you cannot sent your C-Cex NEWB to IDEX.  The only way to transfer between then is via NEWB to NEWB swap but this is not yet enabled.  We are currently having internal discussions of how we can enable this but nothing yet is confirmed.

Title: [ANN] NEWB - The crypto market's dirty little secret
Body: To provide you clarification NEWB tokens exist on the Nxt blockchain (51 million tokens) & Ethereum blockchain (49 million tokens).   NEWB on Nxt is traded on C-Cex exchange NEWB on Ethereum is traded on EtherDelta  At the current time we have not enabled swapping but this will be allowed in the future.  So in the future you will be able to swap between the two blockchains on a 1 to 1 basis.  NEWB_NXT <---> NEWB_ETH  This will also allow taking advantage of arbitrage opportunities.  Newbium is currently the only coin which is multi blockchain listed and traded.

Author: ICOfan
Title: [ANN] NEWB - The crypto market's dirty little secret
Body: The Nov 10 Wall Street Journal proclaimed that the Securities and Exchange Commission is “talking tough on Coin Offerings.”  Initial Coin Offerings (ICOs) that offer a share in profits or have equity features are indeed at risk of securities regulations—but an ICO designed as a utility token (an advance purchase of a product or service) without equity features should not be deterred by threats of securities regulators.  Indeed, most companies may have an opportunity to leverage ICOs to raise funds via advance sales without giving up equity—if they structure their ICO correctly.  This article explains how to do this, with a case study on an “Initial MemberCoin Offering” Blockchain Business Consultants are now working.  Kickstarter and sites like this allow people to buy products and services in advance to support a business launch or expansion legally.  But they are full of restrictions on the type of projects they will support, are for relatively small amounts of funding, and of course charge fees.  A business that can do an advance sale of a product, services or membership and wants to raise millions of dollars may be better off using an ICO with a tradable cryptocurrency token.  For big projects where current and future customers may be eager to help you finance the expansion (with a discounted price offer) but want the flexibility to bail out of buying in down the road (i.e. they need to be able to readily sale their utility token right to buy your service) this is a potentially huge, revolutionary application of blockchain and cryptocurrency.  due to size limit can't post all article, go to bchainconsult.com blog page to read the full article

Author: ICOfan
Title: [ANN] NEWB - The crypto market's dirty little secret
Body: I’ve been trying to figure out how to explain Blockchain, Cryptocurrency, and ICOs in a short elevator pitch.  Got a great suggestion from “Blockchain Business Consultants” (www.bchainconsult.com) I’m sharing here.  If you like it, please feel free to use it.  If you have suggestions to make this better (but not longer), please let me know.  How to Explain Blockchain, Cryptocurrency, and ICOs in one short paragraph Elevator Pitch   A blockchain is a secure distributed ledger or database where past “blocks” of entries are “locked in” so securely that you cannot alter them.  It is not run by a company or any trusted party—but a computer network.  A network of computers reach a consensus on the current block of transactions and once a majority agree, the new block of transactions is locked onto the blockchain database.  It’s a virtually unhackable, highly secure distributed ledger that can replace intermediaries like banks, or any company and authority now relied on as “trusted party” or controller of an information system.  With “Smart contracts” in the blockchain system, executed by the computer network when agreed upon conditions are met, you can conduct transactions without lawyers and middlemen.  Blockchain is used for virtually unhackable digital currency to pay for online transactions (cryptocurrency—like Bitcoin, Ether, others) and for a new means of raising funds:  an “Initial Coin Offering” where you produce a “token” you can trade on a blockchain that, combined with Smart Contracts, provides rights to buyers to use services or buy products.

Author: landomata
Title: [ANN] NEWB - The crypto market's dirty little secret
Body: We also want to add that we have another use case which may even surpass advertising demand.  This use case is tied to chat.newbium.com and is quite innovative.  Users will require NEWB if they wish to make announcements that send mass notifications to all Newbium chat users (site-wide notifications).    Normally on Slack you can use the @channel to notify those on your team which maybe a handful of users or a large group.  In any case this is still much smaller than the total population of slack users.  Now imagine if you could target all users across every slack team with a general announcement that would greatly increase your reach and would be very valuable.  Unfortunate it would also generate much more notifications than there are even now with slack for example.  To control site-wide notification spam users will need to pay to use the function, they will have to pay in NEWB.  The amount of NEWB to use this function will not be as high per say but since many coins need to make important announcements then we foresee strong NEWB demand because of this simple use case.    There are technically no limit to how many site-wide (mass) notifications can be sent but ad space is always limited due to real estate constraint on the site.

Author: landomata
Title: [ANN] NEWB - The crypto market's dirty little secret
Body: We are taking our time because we are working within some constraints such as keeping the distribution very simple and making sure those who receive NEWB will be able to add value to the NEWB market & community.  If we randomly distribute to 50,000 people there is a fair chance that only 15-20% will be really engaged in the NEWB market & community.  The other 80% would not be much help so we need to find ways to filter out this 80%.  If we find these filtering solutions then we can increase the chance to only distribute to those who will really engage in the NEWB market & community.  This is a win/win for everyone in the NEWB market & community.

Author: landomata
Title: [ANN] NEWB - The crypto market's dirty little secret
Body: We are dedicated to Ethereum blockchain but since the backbone of coins.newbium.com is the Nxt/Ardor blockchain it is much easier to build for Nxt/Ardor architecture.  All user accounts on coins.newbium are already accounts on the Nxt/Ardor blockchain.  With Nxt/Ardor we are already build for sidechains functionality.   Keeping that in mind we are focus on the principle of simplicity and providing crypto information is our main purpose.  It makes no sense to build additional features if our main users want only information.  After a year of operation this is very clear to us and we have quietly been conducting R&D to provide this functionality as efficiently as possible.    No matter how you look at it, robots will outdo humans at information generation & distribution.  In a small step towards that direction, we have just finished integrating machine readable functions into https://coins.newbium.com.     We have also been building up our crypto market information database side @ http://newbium.com

Author: LemonAndFriesOne
Title: [ANN] NEWB - The crypto market's dirty little secret
Body: Today I was looking around for data analyses tools and I remembered Newbium.  I decided to go on Newbium.com and see what data I could gather, only thing is the data analysis tools are not quite there.  It'd nice if when I click on a particular coin it would pull up data from several exchanges, blogs, news, etc. and display them all at once in their own seperate sections.  Also, a tool that averages out the values between different sources would be nice, and a rough predictability tool based on probabilities would also be a plus.  Just pointing these things out, because today I actually thought about using a type of market analyses tool and newbium would have fit right into what someone looking for these would need.  Also, what is going on with Nxtty?

Author: landomata
Title: [ANN] NEWB - The crypto market's dirty little secret
Body: Thanks for giving us this critical feedback which we greatly appreciate.  I am not sure how long you have been away but news and coin information on individual coins is provided on https://coins.newbium.com . On http://newbium.com coin market information is processed from all major exchanges to provide individual coin market snapshots.  Fortunately, many platforms and exchanges are already providing analysis tools for you to use, so there shouldn't be difficult for you to locate.  Yes, we can definitely add additional metrics to make the coin information on http://newbium.com more predictive.  Do bear in mind our database will be one year old in 2 months time, as our database evolves then we are able to use that data in more ways.    Newbium is an information platform comprising coin information, market news and objective cryptocurrency market data.  Our aim since the beginning is to make this information available to lay persons as well as professional by stripping out complexity and providing a clear picture of cryptocurrency markets.  Nxtty has been scaled back and we are now focused 100% on Newbium success.

Author: landomata
Title: [ANN] NEWB - The crypto market's dirty little secret
Body: Our user ownership strategy is to initially distribute 12 million NEWB_Nxt tokens.  We have divided Newbium platform users into two user categories, producers & consumers of content on the site.  The rough ratio is 3,000,000 tokens for producers & 7,000,000 tokens for consumers.  The current airdrop is only for 1,000,000 coins distributed to producers who make up our Analyst rank members.   Only after we have fully deployed the user profile page/wallet will we be looking to start distribution to users who are consumers.    The user profile page will also allow us to roll out the reputation system as outlined in our previous post.

Title: [ANN] NEWB - The crypto market's dirty little secret
Body: 1) We shall employ periodic airdrops to spread NEWB distribution across users.  The timing, method and amount for each airdrop will vary.  2) The 1st airdrop will consist of 1 million NEWB_Nxt tokens to users who make up the Analyst Rank.  3) From today, We shall institute user rankings on coin.newbium.com, there will initially be 4 ranking levels.  All users will start at the basic rank called Newb, the highest level at this moment is Oracle.  Oracle Analyst 1st Rank Analyst Newb  4) All users who have made a post or commented from June till December 14th 2016, UTC 00:00 will be elevated to the rank of Analyst.    5) Users will not be able to immediately move their Newb tokens from the coin.newbium wallet.  This is to protect the market balance going forward.  6) The schedule for the 1st airdrop will be communicated over the coming days.

Author: landomata
Title: [ANN] NEWB - The crypto market's dirty little secret
Body: We have recently upgraded the platform with the Newbium Brain foundational layer.  This upgrade integrated the crypto currency market data side of Newbium (newbium.com) with the social information sharing side (coins.newbium.com). As a result of this integration we are now semi-autonomously producing very primitive Crypto Market updates: https://coins.newbium.com/post/2732-litecoin-crypto-market-update-oct-12-2016  These crypto market updates are very primitive at the moment but as time goes by they will become more in-depth and helpful to our users.    The Newbium platform is more than the sum of its parts, like the left and right brains of humans.  Each hemisphere of the human brain functions differently while working together to produce results greater than the sum of its parts.    The aim of Newbium is to provide our users with support tools to make better crypto investment and engagement decisions.  As we build and develop the Newbium platform towards this end the uniqueness of what Newbium is will become clear.

Author: Godson_Mansa
Title: [ANN] NEWB - The crypto market's dirty little secret
Body: Hello Everyone my name is Godson.  i am a long time/term supporter of Newbium, i was one of the first few people to see it's potential and support it, i read the forum everyday and i read the articles from time to time. yet it is important to remember that this is crypto. The best projects don't always make the coins great or profitable, especially when the coin isn't involved in day to day activities. I know this. Look at NXT, XCP vs ETH and Lisk.     Nxt and XCP have way more current capabilities and use than ETH and Lisk but the market value swings towards the latter. DGB is kind of in the middle. What this coin needs is some hype and a MarketMaker, to provide liquidity and make sure we don't get delisted from exchanges. That's my 2 cents. keep supporting good projects.         back to lurking.

Author: baggle
Title: [ANN] NEWB - The crypto market's dirty little secret
Body: My opinion about NEWB_NXT going down is because of the current post bounty.  Actually, investors have put BTC in the project because they believe in it. However, this post bounty "distributes" those BTC to NEWBIUM platform users. Then, investors may think those posting users take the current bounty for a cash machine, and that the project has no more interest and will die.  However, NEWBIUM is a long term investment, people who went in early know it, and are holding. Only few people sell, or because they think the bounty is killing the project, or because they changed their mind about how to make profits (or many other possible reasons).  Even if some users may take NEWBIUM as a cash machine, this doesn't matter too much considering they only are a few, that non original content aren't rewarded, that the higher quality the higher the reward, and that those users are needed (to make the platform known) and will forever exist. This bounty gives datas to NEWBIUM's team to adapt the reputation and reward future system. This also is, if we think in a short term vision, a bad thing, because the team is "loosing money". If you however think long term, you should see this post bounty as an investment, this is a pretty good thing because reward and reputation system will have strong bases, strong enough to last long.  By the way, something to remember is that what will make NEWBIUM successful and profitable on the long term, is NEWBIUM brain. But for this brain to work, there are several steps to cross that can make fluctuate the price. This is where we will see who will panic sell, even maybe at loss. People thinking long term, and believing in the project will be then free to increase their NEWB bags at low price.  Finally, everybody should remember than NEWB_ETH have been distributed, but there is no exchange yet. I guess that NEWBIUM team will do its best to have a good exchange (bittrex currently being targetted), and then to put light spots on those tokens, and necessarly on the project.

Author: landomata
Title: [ANN] NEWB - The crypto market's dirty little secret
Body: Our incentivization system is a combination of a Reward system & Reputation system.  Both the reward & reputation systems will be integrated into https://coins.newbium.com  The reward system will reward those who post original crypto related content.  The reputation system will use gamification to make sure the content produced by posters is the highest quality.  Our system is very similar to Steemit but it will also be different.  Basically, those who produce the best content will be ranked higher on our leaderboard.  The higher your rank the more money you will make.  Those who don't produce good content will not rank and will not be rewarded.  Our aim is to keep the platform simple and user-friendly for everyone while allowing users to post high-quality crypto related content.

Author: baggle
Title: [ANN] NEWB - The crypto market's dirty little secret
Body: Hi,  I first advise you to read the first post, Newbium project is well explained there.  Roadmap : http://www.newbium.com/newbiumwhitepaper.pdf (It really deserves a look).  To be short, Newbium aims to:  Newbium ( http://www.newbium.com/ )is a platforme providing in real time and historical datas about crypto market.  It will also give the possibility to buy and sell coins.  NEWBIUMs are coins which will give revenues as (non-exhaustive list): 1) Paid subscriptions for specialized data/services. 2) Sales of Index products (NxttyACCI). 3) Providing data feeds for third-party plugins (Wordpress), widgets, etc. 4) Providing human generated data feeds to robotic traders, DAO, etc. 5) Access to historical data in Newbium database.  Newbium will propose some kind of "chat" ( http://www.newbium.com/social/ ). The idea there is to offer the possibility to Newbium's users to share their analysis, and to somehow be paid for, by others users. Considering the tiny part of human using or just aware about crypto, it lets predict that millions (not to say billions) might use Newbium. Furthermore, if you consider that Finance world (traders, hedge funds...) will slowly have to move into crypto world... Well, those analysis shared by Newbium users will find their public pretty easily.  You can of course use NEWBIUMs as pure speculative investment, even if i guess long hold is definitely the best.  Finally, Newbium is based on a dual blockchain, NXT and ETH. NEWB-NXT tokens have been sent and already are on c-cex ( https://c-cex.com/?p=newb-btc ). NEWB-ETH tokens currently are being distributed by the team.   My personnal opinion on Newbium is that it's very promising, the project in itself looks sensed and will offer something new and interesting to crypto-world. The team is actually doing good job, and is present to answer questions (here on the forum and on slack). I invested in both blockchains, and i'm already in profits with NEWB-NXT tokens and sure it will the same with NEWB-ETH tokens.   By the way, if anybody sell NEWB-NXT tokens, contact me i'm much interested in

Body: Yes, https://coins.newbium.com will be very similar to Steemit, Facebook, etc as a social media site where anyone can post content.  But keep in mind that we are focused only on crypto related content.  Also we are already a leader in real time crypto market information with the visualization part of newbium.  So with real time crypto market information + crypto related user generated content, we are already seeing something very unique taking shape.  The rewards system is still being fleshed out but it will definitely reward those who provide content.  We have not decided if voting will be used but sharing is one action which is already confirmed.  So users will be rewarded for sharing content to social media even if they are not the original posters of the content.  The reputation system will also be integrated into the rewards system....we intend to build a meritocracy so that only those who provide the best content (analysis, news, information, etc) will have the best ranking.  Although we can see various monetization options our focus at this point is to get the content generation cycle started.  The more high quality content we generate on the platform the more our organic reach increases and the more users we will attract. The more users we have the more we can monetize....revenue streams we have already highlighted are subscriptions and commissions from shapeshift trading.

Title: [ANN] NEWB - The crypto market's dirty little secret

"Just to explain my specificness....im trying to see if its possible to identify when the movers and shakers (whales) are active, and not. And for that, i need an easy on the eye way of expressing these possible patterns, ideally in real-time."  So to reiterate the above, i want to know and identify when market moving size, enters or leaves a given market, in an attempt to ride their coat-tails. I would also need this to be represented on a line graph to easily identify any patterns/ratios, if any.

Author: altsheets
Title: [ANN] NEWB - The crypto market's dirty little secret
Body: ^^^ Please: When you press 'quote' delete all text you are not referring to, thx.  New functions implemented  v0.7.4   The top20 can now be sliced to show only the top:  Top 1  (click for larger)  The past 24 hours of Bitcoin price changes, in one simple image. http://www.newbium.com/beta/top/1/   Top 2  (click for larger)  Bitcoin (BTC) versus Ethereum (ETH) Some people say, they are often moving antiparallel - now you can check that hypothesis visually. http://www.newbium.com/beta/top/2/   Top 10  (click for larger)  The top10 (currently BTC ETH LTC XRP DAO DASH LSK MAID DOGE DGD XEM STEEM) Together they make up 97.42% of the total crypto marketcap. (So the remaining 562 coins (on ranks 11-572) together ... are 38 times smaller!) http://www.newbium.com/beta/top/10/   Top 20  (click for larger)  Not new. The image that you already know. But sometimes it was just too chaotic, that is why - you can also access coins in the acronymlist on the right - and additionally now, with above URLs, can reduce the number. http://www.newbium.com/beta/top/20/   Click, and Doubleclick  In the above graphs, when clicking, the (WOB+CMC+SS) was opened in the same tab, the graph disappeared, made place for the histogram, the "gray Laptop" with CMC data, and the BUY/SELL buttons.  Which is actually not what I personally prefer -  I want to open several coins in one visit.   Solution found and implemented:  CLICK = open in SAME window/tab DOUBLECLICK = open in new tab  The (single)click only works in the acronym list on the right - because otherwise, on tablets  each touch of the screen would immediately open the new page.  The reason is that the Voronoi Tesselation assigns every single pixel of the graph area ... to a coin. So touching any area ... will always open the coin whose curve is nearest to your fingertipp.   Vocabulary:   Voronoi Tesselation?  Some of you might have wondered what the "Show Voronoi" checkbox is for. Now, with the new single BTC curve (it is not necessary but) easier to understand:   (click for larger) (see live on http://www.newbium.com/beta/top/1/ enable 'Show Voronoi')  "A tessellation is the tiling of a plane using geometric shapes, with no overlaps and no gaps."  In maths, "a Voronoi tesselation is a partitioning of a plane into regions based on distance to points", and it is named after Georgy Voronoi.  With that algorithm, any pixel of the whole rectangular graph area can be assigned to the "nearest" curve - and in our case, that allows us to click NEAR a curve, and still HIT a coin. Very practical.   Timing: This is not a new function, but you might not have noticed yet:  Every 5 minutes, the page refreshes itself, automagically.  Why is the auto-refresh useful?  Put it in in a separate small browser window, zoom out (Ctrl-Minus), and leave it open. Then you are among the first who might notice when a top20 market goes boom:   newbium.com   Best of luck in your trading!     EDIT: retweet please - thanks.

Author: landomata
Title: [ANN] NEWB - The crypto market's dirty little secret
Body: NXTTY to Newbium (NEWB) Swap Plan    1) 100,000,000 NXTTY representing 10% of the NXTTY coinbase will be swappable.  100,000,000 NXTTY for 1,000,000 Newbium (NEWB) Tokens.  Ratio - 100 : 1  So if you swap 100 NXTTY you will receive 1 Newbium (NEWB) token.   2) Current holders of NXTTY will be able to swap 20% of their NXTTY holding for Newbium.   3) Anyone who purchases NXTTY on an exchange from April 15 to  May 15th (UTC time - 00:00) will be eligible for 100% NXTTY -> Newbium (NEWB) swap.    NXTTY to Newbium Swap Process    There will be two ways in which you can swap your NXTTY, each will depend on where you currently hold your Nxttycoin.   1) If you are sending the Nxttycoin from your Nxt wallet, then please send the NXTTY you wish to swap to this Nxt address: NXT-WBW9-3KH5-ETZD-BU2V6  The swap ratio is 100 NXTTY for 1 Newbium (NEWB)  So if you send 100 NXTTY you will receive 1 Newbium (NEWB)   2) If you hold your NXTTY on Bter exchange. Author: altsheets
Title: [ANN] NEWB - The crypto market's dirty little secret
Body: Follow-up to this post of yesterday. For the whole post, see the DASH thread. For you, I am extracting from it the ...  WOB explanations pt2  Let me motivate the summing scheme:  Imagine what a buy order means: I am locking my BTC into the order - I cannot spend it anymore for ice cream, or helicopters. Even if I hope to get DASH at a really low price - my order-locked BTC is not only showing my "price hope" - but it is also showing the absolute amount of real money that I had been willing to lock into orders.  Same for sell orders: Transfering my DASH to an exchange is risky, I give up my property in exchange for an IOU. And I declare that I want to sell them. Might be at a really high price only - but I show my willingness to sell them, not using them to buy something, or fund projects, or save for my children - but by offering them in a sell order.  And as both sides get totalled in the same way, we CAN actually compare them. Or rather: We DO compare them ;-)  My own scepticism got smashed when I did cross-comparisons of different coins. They do differ in this new WOB indicator, and they differ much. I suggest you start observing it over time, for 3 very different coins - and you might find out that it will help you to assess how "long-term realistic" the current price of a coin is, compared to our quotient of totals of the (most of the) biggest, available order books world-wide.  I am querying 30+ exchanges! With our current "bittrex bleutrade bter ccex exmo livecoin poloniex yobit" in BTC and 2 fiat currencies - am I sampling enough of your field? [i.e. DASH]   Anecdote: When I tried my simple base calculation for the first time, about 1.5 years ago, and only with the orderbooks of poloniex ... I was surprised to see that LTC stayed totally OB-balanced over a very long period of time - and with varying current prices. As if the total order book volumes ("the whole market"), and the current marketprice ("the day traders") are well-coupled - at least for those "relaxed systems" with high volume, and long past - like Litecoin. (Right now, the situation of LTC looks less rosy, actually. But the better is the enemy of the good, I guess.)  ...  I am interested to see which other knowledge our newbies & pros will be compiling collectively - about all of the most advanced & really successful currencies ... once our 8-steps system is complete. Read the whitepaper & medium blog if you want to. And simply start using the beta already.  May it help your trading!      --> http://www.newbium.com/preview

Author: landomata
Title: [ANN] NEWB - The crypto market's dirty little secret
Body: 1) Newbium (Nxt) tokens exist on the Nxt blockchain and will utilize the Nxt wallet:  https://bitbucket.org/JeanLucPicard/nxt/overview   Newbium (Eth) tokens shall exist on the Ethereum blockchain and utilize Ethereum based wallets such as Mist:  https://github.com/ethereum   Newbium tokens are secured by open sourced and audited wallets.  The Newbium proprietary technology will not be open sourced.  This is the property of the Newbium token holders and we will not give it away to anyone.   2) Actually, we had planned to make an announcement later today regarding the request for escrow members from within the Newbium token holder community.  So only those who send in their Bitcoins would be eligible for escrow membership.  The community would be the deciding factor in who becomes their escrow partners.   Let me be clear...I have been a member of this community for more than two years and have never scammed or had any scam allegations levelled towards me.  This is because I always keep the interest of token holders as my guiding principle.

Author: landomata
Title: [ANN] NEWB - The crypto market's dirty little secret
Body: Further crowdsale details   1) Each BTC address is personalized. Keep it to yourself.  2) One address per depositor, and per token choice (*).  3) Use www.blockchain.info to check your transaction.  4) Double check that your email address is correct.  5) In the next few days, you will get a confirmation email from us.  6) We will have a dedicated page where you can check your status.   (*) Tokens choices are 'Newbium (NXT blockchain)' or 'Newbium (ETH blockchain)' If you want both, submit 2 forms to get 2 BTC addresses to send to. You can re-use your email address.   To be clear: Do not share YOUR bitcoin address, it is given to you only.  If you invite others, tell them to visit www.newbium.com - thank you very much.

Author: landomata
Title: [ANN] NEWB - The crypto market's dirty little secret
Body: The Newbium crowdsale has two options     1) Option one is linked to Newbium (Nxt blockchain) tokens.  This option is non-escrow making it higher risk.  To offset the higher risk for crowdsale participants, Newbium (Nxt) tokens will be distributed immediately on completion of the crowdsale.  If the crowdsale capped is reached before May 31st then Newbium (Nxt) tokens will be distributed before May 31st as well.  Trading of Newbium (Nxt) tokens will begin immediately after the distribution.  2) Option two is linked to Newbium (Ethereum blockchain) tokens.  This option is escrowed making it a lower risk.  Due to the lower risk for crowdsale participants, Newbium (Eth) tokens will be distributed after the crowdsale period has ended.  Trading of Newbium (Eth) tokens will not begin immediately after distribution.  Details 40,000,000 or 40% of tokens are provided in the crowdsale. 20,000,000 Newbium (Nxt blockchain) Tokens & 20,000,000 Newbium (Ethereum blockchain) Tokens.  The crowdsale is capped at USD 600,000  You can purchase Newbium tokens using Bitcoin.

Author: landomata
Title: [ANN] NEWB - The crypto market's dirty little secret
Body: NXTTY to Newbium (NEWB) Swap Plan    1) 100,000,000 NXTTY representing 10% of the NXTTY coinbase will be swappable.  100,000,000 NXTTY for 1,000,000 Newbium (NEWB) Tokens.  Ratio - 100 : 1  So if you swap 100 NXTTY you will receive 1 Newbium (NEWB) token.   2) Current holders of NXTTY will be able to swap 20% of their NXTTY holding for Newbium.   3) Anyone who purchases NXTTY on an exchange from April 15 to  May 15th (UTC time - 00:00) will be eligible for 100% NXTTY -> Newbium (NEWB) swap.    NXTTY to Newbium Swap Process    There will be two ways in which you can swap your NXTTY, each will depend on where you currently hold your Nxttycoin.   1) If you are sending the Nxttycoin from your Nxt wallet, then please send the NXTTY you wish to swap to this Nxt address: NXT-WBW9-3KH5-ETZD-BU2V6  The swap ratio is 100 NXTTY for 1 Newbium (NEWB)  So if you send 100 NXTTY you will receive 1 Newbium (NEWB)   2) If you hold your NXTTY on Bter exchange.  Then please follow the below steps.  A) Withdraw the NXTTY you wish to swap to this Nxt address: NXT-WBW9-3KH5-ETZD-BU2V6  B) Send me a PM containing:        * The withdrawal transaction ID number for your withdrawal transaction to the swap account.       * Your Bter NXTTY deposit account number       * PM mail title - NXTTY to Newbium swap   Swap Timeframe: We have decided to extend the NXTTY to Newbium swap till May 15th UTC time 00:00.   Swap Payout: The Newbium (NEWB) will be sent once the crowdsale is finished.

A reward based system for newbies who are actively creating and sharing valuable data analysis.  Those who post sound investment and trading ideas will inevitably grow their followers and viewer base on the platform.  These followers and viewers can tip the Newbies cryptocurrencies for their valuable service.The more value a Newbie generates for it users the more tips the Newbie will receive from Newbium users.  In addition, Newbies can monetize the content they produce by creating private trading groups within the platform.  To join private groups users will have to pay a subscription fee. +++

Title: [ANN] NEWB - The crypto market's dirty little secret

Author: landomata
Title: [ANN] NEWB - The crypto market's dirty little secret
Body: Yes, aspects of the vision must imbue the name.  We did not choose "noob" because we felt it had more negative connotations than newb.  Many people will describe themselves as newbies at something but not many will call themselves noobs.  I think we both can agree that 99% of the humans on this planet are "not" in crypto at this time.  So if crypto continues down its path to mainstream adoption that would mean the 99% still left to enter this field are in fact, newbies.    Newbium aims to make this transition as easy as possible by providing a platform where the complex cryptocurrency market data is experienced in a simple and intuitive manner.

One of the more frustrating analytical barriers is the lack of raw-trades archives - the kind that do exist for Bitcoin exchanges. If NEWBIUM archives raw trades and allows access for statistical and other aglo-type analyses, that'd be great!

Author: landomata
Title: [ANN] NEWB - The crypto market's dirty little secret
Body: We are more focused on human generated data but this is something we could look at in the future.

Author: Raquel003
Title: [ANN] NEWB - The crypto market's dirty little secret
Body: Hey there! Don't know if this is exactly what you are looking for, but have you checked out the uᴉoɔʇᴉq and cryptocurrency databases on Quandl at https://www.quandl.com/vendors/bnc ?  I realize you mentioned "raw" trades, but figure I'd share this anyway in case it might be helpful to you or others: https://www.quandl.com/data/BNC2 - This shows historical global price indexes for over a thousand cryptocurrency/fiat-currency pairs. Data is taken from more than a hundred trading platforms for crypto/fiat trading pairs. Each trading pair is volume-weighted per exchange, then consolidated using rules-based formulas into market-weighted averages (MWAs).  [I should disclose: I work for Quandl.]
